languages.text:
"От целого осталась только часть,
Предательство истерло остальное.
В мир яви путь ему закрыт навек:
Кошмарам Темный город домом служит.
Забудь. Оставь. Не поминай былое".

languages.text:
"A fragment's all that's left of what was whole,
The rest now worn away by treachery.
Reality for him is out of bounds,
But nightmares in Commorragh find a home,
Depart. Forget. And leave the past alone."

languages.text:
“一度完整之物，如今已只剩下余烬。
其余的一切，早已被背叛消磨殆尽。
对他而言，现实早已无法触达，
而噩梦却已在科摩罗生根发芽。
离开吧，忘记吧，过去的事情就过去吧。”
languages.original_text:
"A fragment's all that's left of what was whole,

But nightmares in Commorragh find a home,
Depart. Forget. And leave the past alone."

languages.text:
«Queda solo un fragmento de lo que era,
tras la cruel erosión de la traición.
La realidad para él no está aquí, sino fuera,
pero los miedos en Commorragh entran en acción.
Márchate y olvida, pues los recuerdos pasado son».
languages.original_text:
"A fragment's all that's left of what was whole,
The rest now worn away by treachery.
Reality for him is out of bounds,
But nightmares in Commorragh find a home,
Depart. Forget. And leave the past alone."

languages.text:
「残されているのは断片だけ
あとは裏切りによりすり減った
彼にとって現実は得難いが
コモラフの悪夢はすべてを受け入れる
旅立ち、忘れろ。そして過去に囚われるな」
languages.original_text:

But nightmares in Commorragh find a home,
Depart. Forget. And leave the past alone."

languages.text:
"Vom Ganzen ein Fragment nur noch besteht,
all der Rest abgetragen vom Verrat.
Die Wirklichkeit lässt ihn nicht mehr hinein,
doch Albträumen ist Heimat Commorragh.
Reist ab. Vergesst. Lasst das Vergang'ne ruh'n."
languages.original_text:
"A fragment's all that's left of what was whole,
The rest now worn away by treachery.
Reality for him is out of bounds,
But nightmares in Commorragh find a home,
Depart. Forget. And leave the past alone."

languages.text:
« Du tout, il ne demeure plus qu'une partie,
Le reste s'est vu érodé par la duperie.
Pour lui, la réalité est hors de portée,
Mais les cauchemars à Commorragh sont installés.
Partez. Oubliez. Et abandonnez le passé. »
languages.original_text:
"A fragment's all that's left of what was whole,

But nightmares in Commorragh find a home,
Depart. Forget. And leave the past alone."

languages.text:
"Bir zamanlarki hâlinden kalmış geriye bir parça,
Kalleşlik tüketmiş gerisini yavaşça.
Hakikâte dönmesi başlı başına bir fantezi,
Oysa karabasanlar Commorragh'ta yaşar rahatça.
Unutsun. Kurtulsun. Geride kalsın mazi."
